  [1]: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Odyssey', 'In this ancient Greek epic poem, wily hero Odysseus endures a grueling ten-year journey home from the Trojan War, facing mythical beasts, vengeful gods, and treacherous seas.', NULL, '0192741462', '9780385059411', 374, NULL, 592, 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/11520387-L.jpg', '/works/OL61982W', NULL, '1989', 'English', NULL, 1, 0, '-homer', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 'public', '2026-03-16 21:44:35', '2026-03-22 20:32:05');
