Dougie, Spoons and the Aquarium Solarium by Jenny Colgan
Acting Strangely by Chris Manby', 'A group of friends navigates love, secrets, and personal struggles in a tight-knit community.', 2004, '0373250746', '9780373250745', 352, NULL, NULL, 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/217111-L.jpg', '/works/OL14907745W', NULL, 'September 1, 2004', 'English', NULL, 1, 0, 'girls-night-in-lisa-jewell', 1, 'openlibrary', NULL, 0, NULL, 'public', '2026-03-16 21:45:54', '2026-03-22 04:26:59');
